        <p class="_2u_body-1">This cookie is essential for our Intercom help system integration and enables the use the intercom help system.</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">This is provided by <a href="https://www.intercom.com/" target="_blank" class="_2u_legal-link">https://www.intercom.com/</a>.</p>
