        <p class="_2u_body-1">This cookie is essential for our Intercom help system integration and enables us to maintain your intercom session.</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">This is provided by <a href="https://www.intercom.com/" target="_blank" class="_2u_legal-link">https://www.intercom.com/</a>.</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">_ga, _gid</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">These cookies are used by our Google Analytics integration and are used to distinguish users.</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">Google gives more information <a href="https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/analyticsjs/cookie-usage" target="_blank" class="_2u_legal-link">here</a>.</p>
