        <p class="_2u_body-1">This cookie is used for our Google Analytics integration and is used to limit requests (throttle the request rate).</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">Google gives more information <a href="https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/analyticsjs/cookie-usage" target="_blank" class="_2u_legal-link">here</a>.</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">_hjid</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">This cookies are used by our Hotjar integration and is used to distinguish users (Hotjar helps us to improve our website to meet your needs).</p>
        <p class="_2u_body-1">Hotjar gives more information <a href="https://help.hotjar.com/hc/en-us/articles/115011789248-Hotjar-Cookies" target="_blank" class="_2u_legal-link">here</a>.</p>
